Objectives
===============

- 100% Systematic investment plan
- Re-balanced on a monthly basis (once a month trades only)
- Backtested for overperformance over passive benchmarks over all tested asset universes
- Minimal optimisation to avoid overfit
- Easy to implement
- Target risk-adjusted metrics:
  - Target Returns (CAGR) 10%
  - Target Volatility 12%
  - Target MaxDD 15%
  - Target Portfolio Turnover X%
